<p class="footnote"><a href="#78c-4_1" name="78c-4_1_target"><sup>1</sup> So in original. Probably should be "take".</a></p>
<!-- field-end:footnote -->
<!-- field-start:footnote -->
<p class="footnote"><a href="#78c-4_2" name="78c-4_2_target"><sup>2</sup> So in original.</a></p>
