<h4 class="note-head">Amendments</h4>
<p class="note-body"><b>2015</b>—Subsec. (d). <plaw congress="114" isprivate="false" number="94">Pub. L. 114–94</plaw> substituted "case of a bank, a savings and loan holding company (as defined in <uscode edition="2015" section="1467a" title="12">section 1467a of title 12</uscode>)," for "case of bank".</p>
