<p class="note-body"><b>2010</b>—Subsec. (b)(1). <plaw congress="111" isprivate="false" number="203">Pub. L. 111–203,</plaw> §985(b)(5)(A)(ii), in concluding provisions, inserted "The order granting registration shall not be effective until such broker or dealer has become a member of a registered securities association, or until such broker or dealer has become a member of a national securities exchange, if such broker or dealer effects transactions solely on that exchange, unless the Commission has exempted such broker or dealer, by rule or order, from such membership." after "are satisfied."</p>
