<p class="note-body">Subsecs. (e) to (h). <plaw congress="111" isprivate="false" number="203">Pub. L. 111–203,</plaw> §929X(c), added subsec. (e) and redesignated former subsecs. (e) to (g) as (f) to (h), respectively. Former subsec. (h) redesignated (i) relating to limitations on State law.</p>
