<!-- PDFPage:299 --><p class="note-body"><b>2002</b>—Subsec. (b)(4)(F). <plaw congress="107" isprivate="false" number="204">Pub. L. 107–204,</plaw> §604(a)(1), added subpar. (F) and struck out former subpar. (F) which read as follows: "is subject to an order of the Commission entered pursuant to paragraph (6) of this subsection (b) barring or suspending the right of such person to be associated with a broker or dealer."</p>
