<p class="note-body"><a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=124&amp;page=1923" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="111" isprivate="false" number="203">Pub. L. 111–203,</plaw> title IX, §975(i), July 21, 2010, <statuteatlarge page="1923" volume="124">124 Stat. 1923</statuteatlarge></a>, provided that: "This section [amending this section and <uscode edition="2015" range="78o-3, 78o-4, and 78q" section="78o-3" title="15">sections 78o–3, 78o–4, and 78q of this title</uscode>], and the amendments made by this section, shall take effect on October 1, 2010."</p>
